>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Otter es un excelente plugin de diseño para Gutenberg</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/artdesignnetwork\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c3769ec21cc8b59224c83aa7894e69cc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c3769ec21cc8b59224c83aa7894e69cc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/artdesignnetwork\" class=\"reviewer-name\">artdesignnetwork</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 23, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Gutenberg es un excelente constructor de páginas, tiene enorme cantidad de recursos en si mismo y agrega valor una selecta cartera de plugin que lo secundan y fortalecen.\n\nUno de estos plugin es Otter, excelente plugin de diseño para Gutenberg que permite multiples opciones.\n\nExitos y felicitaciones a todos los que apoyan y desarrollan este proyecto.\n\nGualberto Magallanes\nArt Design Network</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ra