gs.</li>\n<li>Implemented view window settings.</li>\n<li>Horizontal and vertical axes settings were split into separate groups.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>1.1.4</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Bug with float values has been fixed.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>1.1.3</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Issue with &#8220;fseek warning&#8221; for Google Spreadsheet document source, was fixed.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>1.1.2</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatibility issues with WordPress version 3.6 has been fixed.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>1.1.1</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Active type tab in the charts library was fixed.</li>\n<li>Library styles were updated.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>1.1.0</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Auto population was added for remote CSV file source.</li>\n<li>Ability to hook chart series and data was implemented.</li>\n<li>Ability to upload CSV files from web was implemented.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>1.0.1</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>The bug with CSV file uploading was fixed.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>1.0.0</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>The first version of what wil be the best wp charts plugin.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:2755:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2117369\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2117369\" alt=\"Chart selection\"></a><p>Chart selection</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2117369\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2117369\" alt=\"Chart selection 2\"></a><p>Chart selection 2</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2117359\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2117359\" alt=\"Library\"></a><p>Library</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=2117369\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=2117369\" alt=\"Download\"></a><p>Download</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=2117359\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/visualizer/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=2117359\" alt