(62, 1, '2020-11-02 12:19:09', '2020-11-02 12:19:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>...or something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Sample Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-11-02 12:19:09', '2020-11-02 12:19:09', '', 2, 'http://localhost/miraflores/2020/11/02/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(63, 1, '2020-11-02 12:19:37', '2020-11-02 12:19:37', '<h1>JARDIM MIRAFLORES</h1>		\n			<h2>Um Novo Horizonte</h2>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Ver Filme\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/VR_selo_PT-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/VR_selo_PT-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/VR_selo_PT.png 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" />											\n										<img width=\"450\" height=\"176\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Jardim_3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Jardim_3.png 450w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Jardim_3-300x117.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" />											\n		<h2 data-fontsize=\"20\" data-lineheight=\"32px\" style=\"color: #000000; margin: 0px; font-family: Raleway; line-height: 1.6; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 20px; --fontsize: 20; --minfontsize: 20;\">Jardim Miraflores são três projetos de arquitetura desenhados com pormenor para o conforto dos seus dias: Torre Girassol, Villa Iris e Lotus Living. Edifícios integrados por jardins e piscinas privadas que oferecem uma grande variedade de tipologias adequadas ao seu modo de vida.</h2>		\n										<img width=\"750\" height=\"417\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_Torres-1536x853.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_Torres-1536x853.png 1536w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_Torres-300x167.png 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_Torres-1024x569.png 1024w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_Torres-768x426.png 768w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_Torres.png 1720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" />											\n		<h2 data-fontsize=\"20\" data-lineheight=\"32px\" style=\"color: #000000; margin: 0px; font-family: Raleway; line-height: 1.6; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 20px; --fontsize: 20; --minfontsize: 20;\">Rasgados sobre a paisagem, os edifícios destacam-se pelo desenho de janelas panorâmicas e terraços amplos revestidos de madeira que se abrem sobre a paisagem marítima do estuário do Tejo e os parques florestais envolventes.</h2>		\n										<img width=\"750\" height=\"750\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CE_GIRA04_00_TERRACO_V02_RGB-copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CE_GIRA04_00_TERRACO_V02_RGB-copy.jpg 900w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CE_GIRA04_00_TERRACO_V02_RGB-copy-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CE_GIRA04_00_TERRACO_V02_RGB-copy-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CE_GIRA04_00_TERRACO_V02_RGB-copy-768x768.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" />											\n		<h1 data-fontsize=\"35\" data-lineheight=\"42px\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \'Josefin Sans\'; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 35px; color: #6f7c53; background-color: #ebebd6; --fontsize: 35;\">VIVA DIAS CHEIOS DE LUZ</h1>		\n										<img width=\"750\" height=\"475\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/FAMILY_shutterstock_1107072644.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/FAMILY_shutterstock_1107072644.jpg 1200w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/FAMILY_shutterstock_1107072644-300x190.jpg 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/FAMILY_shutterstock_1107072644-1024x649.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/FAMILY_shutterstock_1107072644-768x486.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" />											\n										<img width=\"488\" height=\"362\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ICONS_geral.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ICONS_geral.png 488w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ICONS_geral-300x223.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 488px) 100vw, 488px\" />											\n		<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">Os três edifícios têm um total de 119 apartamentos, tipologias de T1 a T5, que incluem apartamentos luxuosos com duas penthouses. Espaços amplos com uma relação privilegiada com a paisagem, desenhados para o seu prazer e conforto, todos os dias.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">Os edifícios têm comodidades de estacionamento, com 274 lugares, piscinas privadas e ginásios, bem como áreas comerciais e amplos espaços comuns para benefício do condomínio.</p>		\n										<img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CI02_00_SALA_P14.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CI02_00_SALA_P14.jpg 1920w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CI02_00_SALA_P14-300x169.jpg 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CI02_00_SALA_P14-1024x576.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CI02_00_SALA_P14-768x432.jpg 768w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CI02_00_SALA_P14-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />											\n		<h1 data-fontsize=\"35\" data-lineheight=\"42px\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \'Josefin Sans\'; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 35px; color: #ffffff; --fontsize: 35;\">A ARTE DE VIVER</h1>Os acabamentos são desenhados com qualidade e materiais nobres. As cozinhas estão inteiramente equipadas com recursos técnicos atuais. Todo o conforto e estética da arquitetura contemporânea em apartamentos desenhados para o seu estilo de vida.		\n										<img width=\"750\" height=\"475\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CRIANCA_shutterstock_1534585178.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CRIANCA_shutterstock_1534585178.jpg 1200w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CRIANCA_shutterstock_1534585178-300x190.jpg 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CRIANCA_shutterstock_1534585178-1024x649.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CRIANCA_shutterstock_1534585178-768x486.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" />											\n										<img width=\"369\" height=\"175\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Girassol_3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Girassol_3.png 369w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Girassol_3-300x142.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 369px) 100vw, 369px\" />											\n		<h2 data-fontsize=\"20\" data-lineheight=\"32px\" style=\"color: #000000; margin: 0px; font-family: Raleway; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 20px; --fontsize: 20; --minfontsize: 20;\">Um projeto do gabinete de arquitetura Metro Urbe é um investimento de natureza única em Miraflores.</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">São 15 andares abertos sobre a paisagem, 68 apartamentos com janelas panorâmicas e terraços revestidos com decks de madeira e duas penthouses de luxo.</p>		\n										<img width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CEGIRA01_00_TORRE_2_V04_RGB-1200x675-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CEGIRA01_00_TORRE_2_V04_RGB-1200x675-1.jpg 1200w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CEGIRA01_00_TORRE_2_V04_RGB-1200x675-1-300x169.jpg 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CEGIRA01_00_TORRE_2_V04_RGB-1200x675-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CEGIRA01_00_TORRE_2_V04_RGB-1200x675-1-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" />											\n										<img width=\"369\" height=\"176\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Lotus_3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Lotus_3.png 369w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Lotus_3-300x143.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 369px) 100vw, 369px\" />											\n										<img width=\"369\" height=\"175\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Iris_3.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Iris_3.png 369w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_Iris_3-300x142.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 369px) 100vw, 369px\" />											\n										<img width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/01_CELOTUS01_00_EDIF_004_RGB-copy-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/01_CELOTUS01_00_EDIF_004_RGB-copy-2.jpg 1200w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/01_CELOTUS01_00_EDIF_004_RGB-copy-2-300x169.jpg 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/01_CELOTUS01_00_EDIF_004_RGB-copy-2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/01_CELOTUS01_00_EDIF_004_RGB-copy-2-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" />											\n		<h2 data-fontsize=\"20\" data-lineheight=\"32px\" style=\"color: #000000; margin: 0px; font-family: Raleway; line-height: 1.6; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 20px; background-color: #ebebd6; --fontsize: 20; --minfontsize: 20;\">Dois edifícios desenhados pelo gabinete GJP, Arquitectos Associados, destacam-se pelo desenho singular dos seus espaços.</h2>Lotus Living é uma torre de 9 pisos e 47 apartamentos, com piscina panorâmica no último piso. Villa Iris é um edifício com quatro espaçosos apartamentos. Juntos, oferecem áreas amplas e apartamentos de desenho e configuração únicos.<h1 data-fontsize=\"35\" data-lineheight=\"42px\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \'Josefin Sans\'; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 35px; color: #6f7c53; text-align: center; --fontsize: 35;\">A SUA VIDA NO CENTRO DE TUDO</h1>		\n										<img width=\"1720\" height=\"821\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_1B.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_1B.png 1720w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_1B-300x143.png 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_1B-1024x489.png 1024w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_1B-768x367.png 768w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MAPA_1B-1536x733.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1720px) 100vw, 1720px\" />											\n		<p>O Jardim Miraflores localiza-se numa área residencial que lhe oferece todas as estruturas a que recorre no seu quotidiano, ali mesmo ao seu lado. Miraflores permite-lhe respirar tranquilidade, entre a Natureza e a vibração hipnotizante da cidade.</p><h2 data-fontsize=\"20\" data-lineheight=\"32px\" style=\"color: #000000; margin: 0px; font-family: Raleway; line-height: 1.6; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 20px; --fontsize: 20; --minfontsize: 20;\">A sul a sua casa usufrui de vistas plenas sobre o estuário do Tejo, onde o Mar encontra o Rio, ladeado a este e oeste pelas florestas de Monsanto e do Jamor.</h2>		\n										<img width=\"560\" height=\"560\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/COFFEE_shutterstock_1093104314.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/COFFEE_shutterstock_1093104314.jpg 560w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/COFFEE_shutterstock_1093104314-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/COFFEE_shutterstock_1093104314-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" />											\n										<img width=\"560\" height=\"560\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/BIKE_shutterstock_251685355.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/BIKE_shutterstock_251685355.jpg 560w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/BIKE_shutterstock_251685355-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/BIKE_shutterstock_251685355-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" />											\n										<img width=\"560\" height=\"560\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/BELEM_shutterstock_796822474.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/BELEM_shutterstock_796822474.jpg 560w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/BELEM_shutterstock_796822474-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/BELEM_shutterstock_796822474-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" />											\n										<img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Brochura_PDF_PT-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"79\" height=\"113\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ICON_STAND_VENDAS.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n		<h2 data-fontsize=\"20\" data-lineheight=\"32px\" style=\"color: #000000; margin: 0px; font-family: Raleway; line-height: 1.6; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 20px; background-color: #b3bc9b; text-align: center; --fontsize: 20; --minfontsize: 20;\">VISITE O NOSSO STAND DE VENDAS NO LOCAL, NA AV. CAROLINA MICHAELIS, LINDA-A-VELHA.</h2><p style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: Raleway, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; background-color: #6f7c53;\"><a href=\"tel:+351 215 807 370\" style=\"transition-property: color, background-color, border-color; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; color: #ffffff;\">+351 215 807 370</a>\n<a href=\"mailto:info@jardim-miraflores.com\" style=\"transition-property: color, background-color, border-color; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; color: #ffffff;\">info@jardim-miraflores.com</a></p>\n<p style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: Raleway, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; background-color: #6f7c53;\"><a href=\"https://jardim-miraflores.com/contactos/\" style=\"transition-property: color, background-color, border-color; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; color: #ffffff;\">ENVIAR MENSAGEM</a></p>		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"46\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_KREST-300x46.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_KREST-300x46.png 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/LOGO_KREST.png 308w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n		<p><a href=\"https://www.krestinvestments.com/\" style=\"background-color: #6f7c53; color: #ffffff; transition: color 0.2s linear 0s, background-color 0s ease 0s, border-color 0s ease 0s; outline: 0px; opacity: 0.75; font-family: Raleway, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px;\">www.krestinvestments.com</a></p>©2020 JARDIM MIRAFLORES – TODOS OS DIREITOS RESERVADOS | BY <a href=\"https://www.illusive.p