erraços amplos revestidos de madeira que se abrem sobre a paisagem marítima do estuário do Tejo e os parques florestais envolventes.</h2>		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CE_GIRA04_00_TERRACO_V02_RGB-copy-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CE_GIRA04_00_TERRACO_V02_RGB-copy-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CE_GIRA04_00_TERRACO_V02_RGB-copy-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CE_GIRA04_00_TERRACO_V02_RGB-copy-768x768.jpg 768w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CE_GIRA04_00_TERRACO_V02_RGB-copy.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n		<h1 data-fontsize=\"35\" data-lineheight=\"42px\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \'Josefin Sans\'; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 35px; color: #6f7c53; background-color: #ebebd6; --fontsize: 35;\">VIVA DIAS CHEIOS DE LUZ</h1>		\n										<img width=\"750\" height=\"475\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/FAMILY_shutterstock_1107072644-1024x649.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/FAMILY_shutterstock_1107072644-1024x649.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/FAMILY_shutterstock_1107072644-300x190.jpg 300w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/FAMILY_shutterstock_1107072644-768x486.jpg 768w, http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/FAMILY_shutterstock_1107072644.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" />											\n										<img width=\"488\" height=\"362\" src=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ICONS_geral.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/miraflores/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ICONS_geral.png 488w, http://localhost/miraflore